<subSubSection pageId="213" pageNumber="818" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="213.[172,1380,254,835]" pageId="213" pageNumber="818">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[174,524,681,715]" pageId="213" pageNumber="818">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Ohia Rat has a small fragmented distribution and is not abundant.
</paragraph>
